<i>leads to stress penalties.</i>

466
00:23:08.600 --> 00:23:12.771
<i>Leaving every soul in the crowd</i>
<i>feeling quite ill at ease.</i>

467
00:23:13.397 --> 00:23:18.819
[Ker] In an FA Cup penalty shoot-out.
each team gets five attempts on goal.

468
00:23:18.902 --> 00:23:20.904
And if it's still tied. after that.

469
00:23:20.987 --> 00:23:24.741
the penalty kicks will keep going
until eventually. there's just one winner.

470
00:23:27.202 --> 00:23:28.286
{\an8}[Mac] So I was back in Philly

471
00:23:28.370 --> 00:23:31.790
{\an8}for the FA Cup match
against Nottingham Forest.

472
00:23:32.833 --> 00:23:38.672
And it turned out to be a hell of a game.
and it all came down to penalties.

473
00:23:39.339 --> 00:23:41.508
[Griffiths] <i>Windass. Yes!</i>

474
00:23:41.591 --> 00:23:42.717
<i>Drills it in.</i>

475
00:23:43.635 --> 00:23:46.304
I love penalties. I feel like anyone
that knows me quite well

476
00:23:46.388 --> 00:23:49.307
