I-I love a penalty shoot-out.

477
00:23:49.391 --> 00:23:51.435
For me. there's no pressure
on a penalty shoot-out.

478
00:23:51.518 --> 00:23:54.646
because you as the player.
have more pressure than me.

479
00:23:54.729 --> 00:23:56.815
