480
00:23:56.898 --> 00:23:57.983
<i>-Saved!</i>
-[cheering]

481
00:23:58.066 --> 00:24:00.068
<i>Great save by Okonkwo!</i>

482
00:24:00.777 --> 00:24:03.113
<i>Callum Doyle next. left-footed.</i>

483
00:24:03.196 --> 00:24:06.158
<i>Drills it!</i>
<i>He's really got the atmosphere going.</i>

484
00:24:06.241 --> 00:24:10.120
<i>Hudson-Odoi. 2-2. The tension continues.</i>

485
00:24:10.203 --> 00:24:12.080
<i>Thomason. left-footed. drills it.</i>

486
00:24:12.164 --> 00:24:15.083
<i>Williams steps up. It's in.</i>

487
00:24:15.167 --> 00:24:17.252
<i>Jay Rodriguez steps up.</i>

488
00:24:17.335 --> 00:24:18.795
<i>Oh. it's a good pen.</i>

489
00:24:20.172 --> 00:24:22.007
Just felt like everyone was switched on.

490
00:24:22.090 --> 00:24:24.259
We wanted
to put a bit of fire in their bellies.

491
00:24:24.342 --> 00:24:27.721
wanted to… [stutters] …send a message.

492
00:24:28.388 --> 00:24:30.682
