whether he wants us to make these for him.

554
00:28:23.873 --> 00:28:25.667
-[Gemma] Are you Mike? Are you Mike?
-[Mike] Hey. hiya.

555
00:28:25.750 --> 00:28:27.794
{\an8}-Yes. Yes.
-Gemma. nice to meet you.

556
00:28:27.877 --> 00:28:30.672
{\an8}-Nice to meet you. How are you?
-Look. I come bearing gifts.

557
00:28:30.755 --> 00:28:32.048
{\an8}-Yeah.
-What do you think?

558
00:28:32.132 --> 00:28:34.092
That's cute. Those are from the shirts
that we gave you?

559
00:28:34.175 --> 00:28:35.343
-Yes.
-Yeah.

560
00:28:35.427 --> 00:28:40.223
The mission for me now is
if you do accept us to do them…

561
00:28:40.306 --> 00:28:42.851
-[Mike] Uh-huh.
-…I'm not gonna be just me doing them.

562
00:28:42.934 --> 00:28:47.731
It's gonna be my charity.
as in Ali. my other girls.

563
00:28:48.606 --> 00:28:51.609
I just want people to know
that there's a space for them.

564
00:28:52.235 --> 00:28:54.988
It's just an opportunity
that doesn't happen all the time

565
00:28:55.071 --> 00:28:58.616
for people like me to get another chance.

566
00:28:58.700 --> 00:29:02.287
These would fit in perfectly for us here.

567
00:29:02.370 --> 00:29:06.416
I mean. we-we even have our own little
"Made in Wrexham. Made in Wales" section.

568
00:29:07.500 --> 00:29:11.379
{\an8}Just to help highlight all of the great
things that are made here locally.

569
00:29:12.464 --> 00:29:15.133
We'll find a spot
that we'll put it right in.

570
00:29:15.216 --> 00:29:18.052
and we'll just have…
we'll have all the bears. you know?

571
00:29:18.136 --> 00:29:20.555
-Can I take a picture? [chuckles]
-Yeah. sure.

572
00:29:20.638 --> 00:29:24.559
[Oakley] I'm so proud. like. because
this is one hell of an opportunity.

573
00:29:24.642 --> 00:29:27.228
I was so scared. I was so scared.

574
00:29:27.312 --> 00:29:31.107
'cause I just… I just didn't think
my work was good enough.

575
00:29:31.191 --> 00:29:32.192
[Mike] Oh. no. It's great.

576
00:29:32.275 --> 00:29:34.903
-They're super adorable.
-I don't… What's wrong with me?

577
00:29:36.488 --> 00:29:39.199
I never. ever thought this would happen.

578
00:29:39.282 --> 00:29:41.576
So I think that I am proof

579
00:29:41.659 --> 00:29:44.537
when the community have seen me go

580
00:29:44.621 --> 00:29:48.333
from being so bad to so good.

581
00:29:48.917 --> 00:29:52.253
It does happen to people. It can happen.

582
00:29:52.337 --> 00:29:55.048
And I… And I want that to happen
for more people.

583
00:29:55.924 --> 00:29:58.635
I want my teddy bears
to go to Ryan Reynolds.

584
00:30:00.261 --> 00:30:02.096
I'll get there one day.

585
00:30:02.931 --> 00:30:07.143
[Gemma] Ali. I can't believe it. [laughs]

586
00:30:09.437 --> 00:30:12.273
