611
00:31:20.842 --> 00:31:23.636
On the angle. Kief! Kief. from the angle!

612
00:31:23.720 --> 00:31:25.597
[Griffiths]
O'Brien dropping off diligently.

613
00:31:25.680 --> 00:31:27.724
Now he's got driving forwards
