614
00:31:27.807 --> 00:31:29.434
poor pass by him. though.

615
00:31:29.517 --> 00:31:31.311
and Madsen drives to the edge of the D.

616
00:31:31.394 --> 00:31:32.395
Crowd tell him to shoot.

617
00:31:32.478 --> 00:31:33.980
That's a good ball to Dembele.
who hits it.

618
00:31:34.063 --> 00:31:36.441
Hit the bar! Bounces back out.

619
