633
00:32:13.353 --> 00:32:15.146
[Parkinson]
Fucking hell. Don't laugh at me.

634
00:32:15.229 --> 00:32:17.231
This is a fucking joke performance.
by the way.

635
00:32:17.315 --> 00:32:19.359
[Roberts] I feel like these players
haven't really gotten

