00:32:20.818 --> 00:32:23.947
This feels very much
like a case of survival.

638
00:32:24.030 --> 00:32:25.740
Short corner. Dembele's got blocked.

639
00:32:25.823 --> 00:32:28.660
[Griffiths] Bobbling around in the box.
Sheaf gets a head to it.

640
00:32:29.410 --> 00:32:31.412
Wrexham will get…
Dembele tries an overhead kick.

641
00:32:31.496 --> 00:32:33.039
Just over the bar.

642
00:32:33.122 --> 00:32:34.666
Clewie. you gotta be closer!

643
00:32:34.749 --> 00:32:36.209
