Wrexham have just got to hang in there.

644
00:32:36.292 --> 00:32:38.795
somehow get a hold of this football.
because at the moment.

645
00:32:38.878 --> 00:32:41.214
QPR just look
like they're going to score a second.

646
00:32:41.297 --> 00:32:42.799
[Griffiths] And that is halftime

647
00:32:42.882 --> 00:32:45.718
